1
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,520
Morning breeze blows

2
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,200
Evening rain falls

3
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,800
Cutting short the years

4
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,600
The last blossoms fall

5
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,600
Pear blossom scent

6
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:07,640
Brews the spring colors

7
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:12,240
The wheel of fortune turns at last

8
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,200
Today

9
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,480
you lose

10
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,000
The winner is yet to be decided

11
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,520
Old Wu

12
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,400
Old Wu

13
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:37,360
It's useless

14
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,840
This lock is clearly specially made

15
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,280
Even if you find

16
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,720
an expert thief skilled in lockpicking

17
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:47,400
it would take at least an hour

18
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:49,160
Besides, there are four keyholes here

19
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,160
It requires four keys turned simultaneously

20
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:52,280
to get through

21
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,240
This needle...

22
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,080
why does it look familiar?

23
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,240
What kind of brain do you have?

24
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,520
How can your own stuff not look familiar?

25
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,400
Believe it or not, I'll hit...

26
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:15,160
Our top priority right now

27
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,280
is to open this door

28
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,080
Meiren

29
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,360
Go get my hammer

30
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,320
Go

31
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:31,720
Here

32
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,400
You hit it

33
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,280
The harder, the better

34
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,160
Hit it

35
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,880
Compared to opening doors the normal way

36
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,160
I prefer the most direct method

37
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,360
Young Mistress Tang

38
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:19,280
you really are a walking weapon of mass destruction

39
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,440
I almost forgot

40
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,120
Tangmen Mechanism Arts

41
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,560
are peerlessly exquisite

42
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:25,840
and unmatched by anyone

43
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:27,880
Come on

44
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,920
A night tour of Linggu Temple Pagoda

45
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,040
starts now

46
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:34,960
Young Mistress

47
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,800
I won't go into the pagoda with you

48
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,280
After all, I'd just hold you back

49
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,320
Someone like me

50
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,720
is better suited for logistics

51
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,240
I think

52
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,360
sticking with us

53
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:46,760
is safer

54
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,600
The sword and the bag!

55
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:53,960
Wait for me!

56
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,680
Wait for me!

57
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,920
Rumor has it that inside the pagoda

58
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,560
criminals who committed heinous crimes are imprisoned

59
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,400
They were secretly recruited by the Eastern Depot as Secret Guards

60
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,400
to guard the dossiers inside the pagoda

61
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,480
Their methods are extreme and unscrupulous

62
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,240
and hard to predict

63
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:42,080
This place is a bit eerie.

64
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:44,920
Anyway, I don't feel comfortable.

65
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,440
It's like we are...

66
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,360
...prey that has fallen into a cage.

67
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,520
This is our cage.

68
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:06,240
This place was built upon our life's work.

69
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,040
We will not tolerate your insolence.

70
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,440
We ask not of your origin.

71
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,680
Nor of your destination.

72
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,640
Only if you can get past the three of us...

73
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:15,280
...can you proceed to the top of the tower.

74
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,440
Wu Qiangu.

75
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,520
It has been a long time.

76
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,240
Weird Old Man.

77
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,240
Do you know them?

78
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,680
They were once unforgivable gamblers.

79
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,360
Unlike ordinary people...

80
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,760
...their underground dealings...

81
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,600
...wagered not only gold, silver, and jewels...

82
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:33,080
...houses and fertile fields...

83
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,640
...but also what others cherished most.

84
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,560
Hands, feet, eyes.

85
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,560
Even wives and children.

86
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:40,400
Luring you step by step into their...

87
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,320
...abyss of gambling.

88
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,160
The Imperial Grand Court of Justice...

89
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,560
...arrested them...

90
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,160
...and sentenced them to death by a thousand cuts.

91
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,320
But due to their mastery of Yin and Yang and Feng Shui...

92
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,640
...the Eastern Depot secretly saved them...

93
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,640
...and recruited them as Secret Guards...

94
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,880
...to serve under their command.

95
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,600
Who would have thought...

96
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,200
...they would be used in a place like this.

97
00:07:57,880 --> 00:08:00,720
Years ago, I wanted to challenge you.

98
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:03,800
Who knew you'd do the foolish deed of severing your own hand?

99
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,000
Now I'll have to go easy on you.

100
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,800
After all these years...

101
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,960
...you haven't changed a bit.

102
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:15,320
Still so obsessed with gambling.

103
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:17,120
Didn't you once experience it too?

104
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:19,560
How could you forget our trials now?

105
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,280
Green Ghost.

106
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,120
It is up to you...

107
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:24,160
...to show them our pleasure.

108
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,720
Looking at your faces...

109
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,840
...you do not look like those who use street gambling tricks.

110
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,400
Why don't we play something simple?

111
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,800
How can you guarantee...

112
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,560
...that you won't cheat?

113
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,760
Since Senior Wu Qiangu is here...

114
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,400
...why would I teach a fish to swim?

115
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:14,120
I prefer to let luck decide the winner.

116
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,880
Isn't that more exciting?

117
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:17,800
The rules?

118
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,280
Before we begin...

119
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,680
...let's make the rules clear.

120
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:21,920
It's very simple.

121
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,600
The heavens have the Five Elements:

122
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,760
Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, and Earth.

123
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,120
They evolve with time to form all things.

124
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,640
Metal overcomes Wood, Wood overcomes Earth, Earth overcomes Water...

125
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,160
...Water overcomes Fire, and Fire overcomes Metal.

126
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:34,120
Metal corresponds to White, Wood to Green...

127
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:37,680
...Water to Black, Fire to Red, and Earth to Yellow.

128
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,920
Green Ghost will deal the cards.

129
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,440
Two cards to each person.

130
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,680
Each will choose one card from them.

131
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:46,000
The winner is decided by the Five Elements cycle of destruction.

132
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,480
Best two out of three.

133
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,320
Isn't that fair?

134
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,560
This is indeed a matter of luck.

135
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:54,920
What do you want to bet?

136
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,600
A secret.

137
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,200
I want to know...

138
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,240
...your true purpose for coming here.

139
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,440
This game is simple.

140
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,800
It is manageable enough...

141
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,200
...for me to play.

142
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,840
You are too humble, Senior.

143
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,040
Since it is about luck...

144
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,920
...I won't hesitate.

145
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:40,040
Let me see your luck then.

146
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,880
I won.

147
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,040
Water overcomes Fire.

148
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,200
The Weird Old Man has good luck.

149
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,760
If he had chosen Wood...

150
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,240
...the result might have been different.

151
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,000
Senior is off to a winning start.

152
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:56,200
Win one more round against me, and victory is yours.

153
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,040
Continue.

154
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,640
Let's go.

155
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,960
Who gave him such confidence?

156
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,880
This round,

157
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,680
as long as Old Wu draws a Wood card that overcomes Earth,

158
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:29,560
we are sure to win.

159
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,560
Although it involves luck,

160
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:34,720
gambling also requires a cool head.

161
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,840
Your attempt to goad me

162
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,280
is a bit shallow.

163
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:46,880
I've said it before,

164
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,640
this is a game of luck.

165
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,680
One defends, one kills.

166
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:58,520
A draw.

167
00:11:59,040 --> 00:11:59,840
Then,

168
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:02,040
we enter the deciding round.

169
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,840
Zhang Shaoqing,

170
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:04,920
Battalion Commander Yuan,

171
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,320
Commissioner Shen,

172
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,760
take your men

173
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,080
and follow me into the tower to investigate.

174
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,040
The rest of you, thirty guard the entrance,

175
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,480
thirty patrol the perimeter.

176
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,600
If you find anything suspicious,

177
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,480
kill on sight.

178
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,120
If after two hours,

179
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,320
I have not emerged,

180
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,840
all Embroidered Uniform Guards here

181
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,000
must rush into the tower to assist.

182
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,200
Yes, sir.

183
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:35,280
Wait.

184
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,800
What is it, Senior?

185
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:40,640
I want to

186
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,160
raise the stakes.

187
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:48,000
Knowing others' secrets is your joy.

188
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,760
Gambling is a two-way street.

189
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,000
Naturally, I

190
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,880
also want to claim my joy.

191
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,920
If I win this round,

192
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,720
I want...

193
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:01,800
You want me?

194
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,240
It is your face.

195
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:07,880
I see your skin is smooth and fine.

196
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:10,040
If I were to peel it off

197
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,760
and give it to Yu Meiren here,

198
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,800
she would surely be delighted.

199
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:15,760
Such a handsome face

200
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,640
to make a skin for a puppet,

201
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,840
it really is excellent material.

202
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,480
Since the game has already begun,

203
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,560
I have no reason

204
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:31,520
to refuse any fair terms.

205
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,880
I will draw first.

206
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,200
Please, Senior.

207
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,400
Old Wu, calm down!

208
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,000
Is he crazy?

209
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:15,800
No.

210
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:18,000
He has seen through the game.

211
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:31,720
I lost.

212
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,240
We won.

213
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,360
We won, right?

214
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,120
We won, we won.

215
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,280
Every time you drew a card,

216
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:39,280
Green Ghost

217
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,840
would stand on our side.

218
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:43,200
Seemingly following rules and waiting

219
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:44,800
to prevent us from cheating.

220
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:45,800
In reality,

221
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:49,000
it was to give Red Ghost opposite us

222
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,840
a signal.

223
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:52,080
You love your appearance,

224
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,440
and the bronze mirror you carry

225
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,640
happens to be able to see

226
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,200
the signals Red Ghost sends you.

227
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,120
In the first round,

228
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:00,040
you gave me a taste of success first,

229
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,320
to test me.

230
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,800
When you were sure you had me,

231
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,640
in the second round,

232
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:08,520
you applied fear and pressure,

233
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:12,000
trying to make me panic.

234
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,280
I didn't see her

235
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,600
giving any hints.

236
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,200
One is Water.

237
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,280
Two is Fire.

238
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,520
Three is Wood, Four is Metal, Five is Earth.

239
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:22,800
Did you notice

240
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:25,480
her hand?

241
00:15:27,520 --> 00:15:29,200
A veteran is a veteran.

242
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,400
You had already seen through everything,

243
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,920
just disrupting their rhythm and cheating.

244
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:36,480
The true meaning of this gamble,

245
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,560
isn't it just about luck?

246
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:42,440
You actually used luck

247
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,040
in the deciding round.

248
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:45,560
How could it be pure luck?

249
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:48,040
Those who can send messages the same way

250
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,520
aren't just you people.

251
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,640
Are you ready now

252
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:57,000
to give me your face skin?

253
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:59,760
When you peeled off others' faces,

254
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:02,200
you never hesitated.

255
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,120
A bet is a bet.

256
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,160
Black Ghost.

257
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,560
The Tang Clan's Record of Villains clearly states:

258
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:09,800
Beautiful appearance, jealous nature.

259
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,360
Likes collecting beautiful skins,

260
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,680
cannot tolerate others' beauty.

261
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,640
Today, the light of justice offers a chance.

262
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:15,800
My sword

263
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,360
is already thirsting.

264
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,760
Gambling on luck and greed

265
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:35,800
only leads to the karmic cycle.

266
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,360
When gambling luck runs out,

267
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,440
you will pay double the price.

268
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:44,160
If you aren't prepared to sacrifice for the gamble,

269
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,200
how are you fit

270
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,520
to live by gambling?

271
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,240
Forget it.

272
00:17:00,680 --> 00:17:01,960
Without this face skin,

273
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:05,240
what difference is there from being dead?

274
00:17:07,840 --> 00:17:09,040
This cage,

275
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,240
I'm tired of staying in it too.

276
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,040
To view a single failure

277
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:18,800
as a humiliating disgrace,

278
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:23,760
is truly arrogant, narrow-minded, and pathetic.

279
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:25,600
Reap what you sow.

280
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:28,280
Gentlemen, please.

281
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,200
I am different from her.

282
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,440
I won't entrust winning or losing

283
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,280
to luck.

284
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,280
Hold on.

285
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,600
Wu Qiangu has already gambled one round.

286
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:39,200
We need to switch people.

287
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,360
As for who to switch to,

288
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,080
I think this is what

289
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,320
you should be weighing now.

