00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:47,840
Secret reports

574
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:48,680
Secret reports

575
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:49,360
I can recite them

576
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:51,440
I can recite them

577
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,400
I can recite them

578
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,240
18th year of Chenghua

579
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,360
fourth day of the fourth month

580
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,640
the demonic hour of You

581
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:58,240
Eastern Depot eunuch

582
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:02,120
This is the record of what we have done recently

583
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:07,600
Meiren

584
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:09,560
Go check their mental state and condition quickly

585
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,680
These people can read characters,

586
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,720
but they cannot comprehend the meaning.

587
00:34:25,680 --> 00:34:26,800
They look like adults,

588
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:28,040
but their behavior

589
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:30,320
resembles that of five or six-year-olds.

590
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,520
But they weren't born this way.

591
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,360
It was caused by poisoning.

592
00:34:35,680 --> 00:34:37,280
That's why they've lost their minds to this extent.

593
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:39,280
They can only read silently,

594
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,800
tools for reciting and memorizing.

595
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:42,280
There is nothing easier to control

596
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:44,200
than emotionless, demented living people.

597
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,760
If they are discovered,

598
00:34:46,680 --> 00:34:47,680
they are simply killed.

599
00:34:47,680 --> 00:34:48,680
Dying with the secrets,

600
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,360
so no one will ever know.

601
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:52,440
If they are found alive,

602
00:34:52,480 --> 00:34:54,360
one just claims they are demented.

603
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:57,360
Everything they say

604
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,400
won't be believed.

605
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,800
You are the steward here.

606
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,960
A mute.

607
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,120
Truly an absolute defense.

608
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:25,840
No.

609
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:29,080
I can roughly guess what he means.

610
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:31,280
He is only responsible for these monks'

611
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,320
basic daily needs.

612
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:33,760
He ignores everything else.

613
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:35,400
Master Konghui passed away today.

614
00:35:35,720 --> 00:35:37,160
These people are disguised as monks

615
00:35:37,240 --> 00:35:38,600
so when the Buddhist relics are enshrined,

616
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:39,680
no one will be suspicious.

617
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,200
Am I right?

618
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:45,240
Raising humans like livestock.

619
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,720
The Eastern Depot actually committed

620
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:49,320
such unconscionable acts.

621
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,960
Nominally exposing treacherous officials,

622
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,880
but in reality, all are unjust cases.

623
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:54,240
Eliminating dissidents, murdering the loyal.

624
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,240
After which of their deeds

625
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:57,880
would they ever show remorse?

626
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:00,160
They probably enjoy it instead.

627
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,520
Under the current circumstances,

628
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:03,520
we can't take the people with us.

629
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:04,680
The secret reports...

630
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,240
we can't take them all either.

631
00:36:10,680 --> 00:36:11,320
This is a knockout drug.

632
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:13,440
Blow it in front of all of them,

633
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,880
and we can take the remaining secret reports.

634
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:17,120
Let's split up.

635
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:17,880
Hurry up.

636
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:18,840
So many things...

637
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,640
take as much as we can.

638
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:20,000
Okay.

639
00:36:54,680 --> 00:36:55,680
I've taken a brief look.

640
00:36:56,120 --> 00:36:57,920
The secret reports here aren't from the Eastern Depot.

641
00:36:58,320 --> 00:37:00,200
Instead, they are investigations into the Western Depot.

642
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:04,880
They must have arrived.

643
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:05,960
A battle is unavoidable today.

644
00:37:06,120 --> 00:37:07,280
Remember our agreement.

645
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:08,080
Do not linger in battle.

646
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:08,720
Do not get killed.

647
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:09,200
Do not get caught.

648
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:09,880
You are not allowed to die.

649
00:37:10,080 --> 00:37:10,760
Escape with all your might.

650
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,000
Especially you, Young Mistress.

651
00:37:13,160 --> 00:37:13,560
Don't worry.

652
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:14,840
I'm injured today.

653
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:16,600
And I want to stay alive to go home for dinner.

654
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:18,360
Then leave it to me for now.

655
00:37:19,120 --> 00:37:20,200
Be careful, Old Wu.

656
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:29,360
My lords.

657
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,520
What took you so long?

658
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:34,160
Wu Qiangu.

659
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,000
Surrender immediately.

660
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:38,600
Lord Yin.

661
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:40,480
Leave Yin Feng to me.

662
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:42,440
You are injured.

663
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:45,160
Do you plan to cripple your martial arts to get married?

664
00:37:46,080 --> 00:37:47,240
For a brute like this,

665
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,520
I alone am enough.

666
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,920
Such arrogant words.

667
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:52,640
A weak little woman thinks she can contend with me?

668
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,080
It seems this lord...

669
00:37:54,920 --> 00:37:55,920
...is not married yet, right?

670
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,200
How did you know?

671
00:37:58,960 --> 00:38:01,120
It's obvious you've never seen how formidable a woman can be.

672
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,200
You look like a fool.

673
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:03,280
You!

674
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,560
Little lunatic.

675
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:06,120
We meet again.

676
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:07,400
Zhang Shaoqing.

677
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:08,840
It's only been six hours.

678
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:09,960
And you miss me already?

679
00:38:11,080 --> 00:38:12,160
If you want to say something...

680
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,760
...like "arresting me" or other nonsense,

681
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:14,960
just save it.

682
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:17,120
It's more satisfying to let our blades do the talking.

683
00:38:17,320 --> 00:38:18,080
You're overthinking it.

684
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,520
I wanted to ask you,

685
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:22,120
can your injury withstand my blade?

686
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,080
Have you heard of a scabbard?

687
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:26,720
Today I'll capture you, you indecent person.

688
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:29,120
Everyone, be careful.

689
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:14,560
You actually didn't fall for the Illusion Magic.

690
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:22,640
By the way,

691
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:25,120
your name is Shen Youzhi.

692
00:39:25,720 --> 00:39:28,640
Your Godfather is Shang Hua.

693
00:39:29,560 --> 00:39:30,840
I originally thought

694
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:34,360
you were a rich playboy born with a silver spoon.

695
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:35,160
But it turns out,

696
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:39,240
you are just a tool cultivated by Shang Hua.

697
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,320
Sorcerer!

698
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:42,040
Godfather treats me like his own son.

699
00:39:42,600 --> 00:39:44,040
I won't allow you to sow discord.

700
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:03,400
Lord Yin.

701
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,600
You've fallen for the Illusion Magic.

702
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:14,120
I didn't expect the Grand Court of Justice...

703
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:15,200
...to have such excellent blade skills.

704
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:17,480
This little woman's swordplay is truly exquisite.

705
00:40:17,680 --> 00:40:18,640
Have you drawn all the moves?

706
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:20,400
Rest assured, my lord, I am drawing them.

707
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:22,360
We can study them together tomorrow.

708
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,800
Me, sowing discord?

709
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,920
What has Shang Hua ever given you?

710
00:40:38,200 --> 00:40:39,760
He hasn't even given you

711
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,040
the simplest hug.

712
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:43,080
Under the banner of "for your own good,"

713
00:40:43,680 --> 00:40:45,800
he arranged everything for you.

714
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:48,160
Every decision in your life...

715
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:49,120
...which one...

716
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:51,560
...did you make yourself?

717
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:53,320
I am different from them.

718
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:54,560
These people...

719
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:56,560
These people...

720
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:01,160
Compared to them,

721
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:03,480
you are nothing but

722
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:06,120
a more expensive puppet.

723
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:07,880
This time,

724
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:11,360
you should thank Wang Zhi.

725
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:13,200
For your operation this time,

726
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,840
that old thing Shang Hua...

727
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:17,680
...will inevitably send his precious godson to gain experience.

728
00:41:18,720 --> 00:41:19,720
When that time comes,

729
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:22,560
please look after him, everyone.

730
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,520
This is Shen Youzhi's secret report.

731
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,000
Please accept it with my compliments.

732
00:41:43,840 --> 00:41:44,520
My Lord

733
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:47,080
These are the children I recently bought.

734
00:41:47,240 --> 00:41:48,160
Their backgrounds

735
00:41:48,280 --> 00:41:49,320
have been investigated thoroughly.

736
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:50,640
There will be no future trouble.

737
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:55,920
The good-looking girls

738
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:57,640
will be sent to Blossom Pavilion for training.

739
00:41:58,240 --> 00:41:59,640
When they are older,

740
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:01,440
we will decide where to place them.

741
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,160
Remind Mistress Hua

742
00:42:03,640 --> 00:42:06,480
to replenish the moles in the officials' residences.

743
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:08,760
Yes, my Lord.

744
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:10,720
Among these children,

745
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:12,920
is there anyone to your liking?

746
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:15,640
Judging by appearance alone,

747
00:42:16,600 --> 00:42:18,080
how can one distinguish good from bad?

748
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:27,880
Whoever can survive for half an incense stick's time,

749
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:29,880
will be rewarded with two bowls of rice

750
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:31,840
and thirty taels of silver.

751
00:42:32,520 --> 00:42:33,840
May I choose not to participate?

752
00:42:34,480 --> 00:42:35,040
What?

753
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:36,960
I've seen gentry raise large dogs like these.

754
00:42:37,160 --> 00:42:38,320
They can rival starving wolves.

755
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:40,160
For two bowls of rice and thirty taels of silver,

756
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:41,280
to risk one's own life...

757
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,080
it is not worth it.

758
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:44,160
If it could ensure a lifetime of food and clothing,

759
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:46,000
then it might be worth risking my life.

760
00:42:46,600 --> 00:42:48,000
Whose child is he?

761
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:48,960
Answering my Lord,

762
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,560
he is a child of the Shen family.

763
00:42:54,400 --> 00:42:55,720
Between you and him,

764
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:58,120
where would fatherly affection come from?

765
00:42:58,520 --> 00:43:00,000
Do you think you are special?

766
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:03,040
Wang Zhi didn't just kill a wolf.

767
00:43:03,120 --> 00:43:05,000
He killed all the children too.

768
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:08,440
You wanted a life of luxury.

769
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:10,400
He gave you wealth and honor.

770
00:43:11,480 --> 00:43:12,440
Between you two,

771
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:14,840
it has always been just a transaction.

772
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:20,640
Youzhi.

773
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:23,200
What books have you been reading lately?

774
00:43:23,840 --> 00:43:24,640
Answering Godfather,

775
00:43:25,120 --> 00:43:26,720
I have been reading *Zuo Zhuan*.

776
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:28,000
*Selections of Refined Literature*.

777
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:31,320
*Selections of Refined Literature*, Volume 45.

778
00:43:31,640 --> 00:43:32,800
*Reply to the King of Chu*.

779
00:43:33,200 --> 00:43:35,640
King Xiang of Chu asked Song Yu:

780
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:37,840
"Sir, is there a flaw in your conduct?"

781
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:41,040
"Why do the common people praise you so little?"

782
00:43:41,400 --> 00:43:42,720
Song Yu replied:

783
00:43:43,160 --> 00:43:45,600
"Yes, indeed there is."

784
00:43:46,160 --> 00:43:47,960
"I hope Your Majesty will pardon my offense"

785
00:43:48,280 --> 00:43:49,800
"and allow me to finish my words."

786
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:52,760
"A sage has magnificent thoughts and extraordinary conduct,"

787
00:43:53,040 --> 00:43:54,160
"standing aloof and alone."

788
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:56,360
"The common people of the world,"

789
00:43:56,520 --> 00:43:59,240
"how can they understand what I do?"

790
00:44:05,160 --> 00:44:06,840
You have never disappointed me.

791
00:44:07,280 --> 00:44:08,360
Then do you know

792
00:44:08,560 --> 00:44:10,800
why I named you Youzhi?

793
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:12,720
The people may be made to follow,

794
00:44:13,160 --> 00:44:14,560
but not to understand.

795
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:19,000
Shang Hua believes in power.

796
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:20,320
Power

797
00:44:20,640 --> 00:44:22,920
is everything he wants.

798
00:44:23,280 --> 00:44:24,200
Shen Youzhi,

799
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:25,600
you

800
00:44:26,480 --> 00:44:29,120
are the extension of his power and desire.

801
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:31,200
He only needed to find

802
00:44:31,520 --> 00:44:34,520
someone to perfectly inherit his mantle.

803
00:44:36,640 --> 00:44:37,840
I am not his tool.

804
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:43,320
But to him, I am more than a transaction.

805
00:44:43,600 --> 00:44:43,920
I...

806
00:44:44,280 --> 00:44:44,600
I...

807
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:47,800
Who am I?

808
00:44:48,680 --> 00:44:50,880
Wu Qiangu, oh Wu Qiangu.

809
00:44:51,720 --> 00:44:52,720
I am not...

810
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:56,680
You are truly a sinful person.

811
00:45:06,720 --> 00:45:07,760
Lu Songshi.

812
00:45:07,760 --> 00:45:08,560
Lord Yuan.

813
00:45:08,880 --> 00:45:09,640
What a coincidence.

814
00:45:09,960 --> 00:45:11,480
In such a life-and-death drama,

815
00:45:11,840 --> 00:45:13,280
why are you so keen on participating?

816
00:45:13,760 --> 00:45:14,680
I don't know either.

817
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:17,440
Perhaps I am the one chosen by Heaven.

818
00:45:18,680 --> 00:45:19,440
Wrong.

819
00:45:21,960 --> 00:45:23,640
I am the one chosen by Heaven.

820
00:45:23,640 --> 00:45:26,520
Then Lord Yuan truly has good fortune.

821
00:45:31,480 --> 00:45:32,640
Miss, are you alright?

822
00:45:33,240 --> 00:45:34,480
I'll treat you to roast duck back in the capital.

823
00:45:38,120 --> 00:45:38,680
Who goes there?

824
00:45:39,760 --> 00:45:40,680
Japanese ninjas.

825
00:45:42,280 --> 00:45:42,800
Japanese people?

826
00:45:42,960 --> 00:45:43,720
Eunuch Lord Wang's secret guards.

827
00:45:43,720 --> 00:45:45,280
My mission is to monitor Shen Youzhi and Zhang Yi.

828
00:45:45,320 --> 00:45:46,000
Hurry up and leave!

829
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:46,560
Go, go, go!

830
00:45:58,560 --> 00:46:00,040
Don't think you can escape!

831
00:46:00,360 --> 00:46:01,440
Why are you fine?

832
00:46:01,800 --> 00:46:03,200
Because I'm immune to poison.

833
00:46:22,520 --> 00:46:22,960
Let's go!
